summary: An ordinance relating to the repairing of the sea wall on Alki Avenue and Harbor Avenue Southwest; authorizing and directing the Board of Public Works to make said repairs; appropriating money therefor from the Emergency Fund; transferring money from the appropriating authorized by Ordinance No. 56505 for repairing sea wall on Alki Avenue and Harbor Avenue Southwest and included in the 1929 tax levy to the Emergency Fund and declaring the emergency therefor.
